OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FA rather
OL,6,Fcloudy but mild night, with occasional
OL,7,Frain, mainly in the north and west but
OL,8,Falso over hills in the south. A
OL,9,Fblustery night, especially in the
OL,10,Fnorth with coastal gales developing in
OL,11,Fthe northwest.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTuesday:FCloud will gradually break up
OL,14,Fto bring a sunny afternoon across much
OL,15,Fof England and Wales. Staying cloudy
OL,16,Fand windy for Scotland and Northern
OL,17,FIreland with further outbreaks of rain.
